# Tests — OSS-02 EarlyDeliveryException og EuBindingPeriodEnd

> Include: ../oss02.catala_da

> Using Oss02 as T

### Tidlig leverance gælder

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEarlyDeliveryApplies:
  oss02 scope T.EarlyDeliveryException

scope TestEarlyDeliveryApplies:
  definition oss02.has_first_eligible_delivery equals true
  definition oss02.notification_on_or_before_tenth_of_month_after_first_delivery equals true
  assertion oss02.use_first_delivery_date_as_effective = true
```

### Tidlig leverance gælder ikke

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEarlyDeliveryNotApplies:
  oss02 scope T.EarlyDeliveryException

scope TestEarlyDeliveryNotApplies:
  definition oss02.has_first_eligible_delivery equals true
  definition oss02.notification_on_or_before_tenth_of_month_after_first_delivery equals false
  assertion oss02.use_first_delivery_date_as_effective = false
```

### Bindingsperiode slutår: valgår 2026 → 2028

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestBindingEndYear:
  oss02 scope T.EuBindingPeriodEnd

scope TestBindingEndYear:
  definition oss02.calendar_year_of_identification_choice equals 2026
  assertion oss02.binding_period_end_year = 2028
```
